## Noncommercial Purposes

In exercising rights under this license, you may not pursue a purpose or
have an application that constitutes, in the sole discretion of licensor,
a **commercial purpose** (other than as set out in the Exceptions).

A purpose or application constitutes a commercial purpose when it is
packaged, distributed, or offered to provide commercial services or for
commercial advantage or private monetary gain. When in doubt, assume a
purpose constitutes a commercial purpose.

### Exceptions

**Charitable purposes.** A purpose or application constitutes a charitable
purpose when it furthers the charitable, educational, scientific, or
medical advancement of humankind. When in doubt, assume a purpose does not
constitute a charitable purpose.

**Licensor's permission.** Licensor may permit a purpose or application
that otherwise constitutes a commercial purpose under this agreement on
such terms as licensor sees fit.

